    "description": "Inspired by Kingdom<br><br>They grew every night, increasing in numbers and consuming everything in their sight.<br>Ruined country, scattered population, nowhere to go.<br>The light will give you time, delaying your inevitable fall.<br>Defend at night until sunrise just to prepare for another tougher night.<br>Dark will descends stronger until everything is consumed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A 2D pixel art side-scrolling resource management with some action and looting.<br></li><li> In the morning you can take a little bit of a breather to prepare and do a little bit of exploring in this small world.<br></li><li> In the night, protect yourself in your base from the shadow creatures looking to consume everything.<br></li><li> Upgrade your equipment or give them to your people to increase your defenses.<br></li><li> Discover hidden and unique artifacts to equip it that would help you in your journey.<br></li><li> Fight back against the shadow creatures and kill their monarchs.</li></ul>",
